import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' import { fetchData } from '../services/api' export default function Home() { let [products, setProducts] = useState([]); useEffect(() => { async function getProducts() { let data = await fetchData(); setProducts(data.products); } getProducts(); }, []) return (
{/* CAROUSEL SECTION */}
{/* PRODUCT SECTION */}
{products.map(product => (
{/* Title */}
{product.title}
{/* Rating */}
{"⭐️".repeat(Math.floor(product.rating))} {"☆".repeat(5 - Math.floor(product.rating))} ({product.rating})
{/* Price */}
₹{product.price * 90}
{/* Expandable Details */}
View Details

Brand: {product.brand}

Category: {product.category}

Stock: {product.stock}

{product.description}

{/* Button */}
))}
) }
